long_description: Use the ripstop polyester Big Agnes Rabbit Ears 4 footprint underneath your Rabbit Ears 4 tent to protect it from wear and abrasion during your outdoor adventures. Precise fit helps prevent pooling of water under tent during wet weather. Webbing stake-outs at tent corners provide easy attachment.
